women—Democrat,  Republican  and  Independent—have  brought  a  unique  and  valu-
able perspective to the decision making process that is our responsibility. 

Whether determining the probable cause of an accident, recommending safety im-
provements, or deciding on federal enforcement actions, we routinely joined together 
with one objective in mind, to raise the standard of safety within our Nation’s trans-
portation community. 

